These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, daffodil, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, may, march
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower         | sunflower      | azalea | orchid | daffodil |
| Birthday   | may | july  | april   | march    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, snake, mouse
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
House: cottage, wooden, colonial, tower
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
2. the owner of the mouse is the mexican##1
3. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
5. the tower house is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the horse##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Pet         | mouse | snake   | horse | ferret  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| House     | tower        | colonial  | wooden    | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, frog, rabbit
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, backgammon, chess
1. the owner of the rabbit is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the frog is between the person eating kiwi and the owner of the goldfish##2
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Pet   | chinchilla  | rabbit | frog   | goldfish  |
| Game     | chess      | whist | backgammon | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, black, green
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge
1. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who likes green is the person playing whist##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes black is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Color   | black  | green      | blood-red        | lavender     |
| Game         | backgammon | whist | bridge | mah-jongg   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, banana, onion, spinach
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, security-guard, designer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person eating spinach is the designer##1
2. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the designer##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the designer##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the fisherman is on the far left##1
7. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
8. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | eggplant   | spinach   | onion | banana |
| Job         | fisherman      | designer | dressmaker      | security-guard |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

