.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lemon, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, comedy, sports
House: victorian, palace, futuristic, gothic-revival
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the victorian house is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the palace house##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon   | pepper      | kiwi       | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports | comedy     | scientific |
| House     | gothic-revival     | palace  | victorian | futuristic |

