.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
4 different games are played: go, chess, snooker, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person driving the roller is the person playing go##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person playing bridge and the person driving the ship##2
3. the person playing bridge is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person playing go is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Game   | snooker     | chess | bridge   | go     |
| Transport           | ship | motorbike         | subway         | roller |

