.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, vegafina, alhambra, baccarat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, action, zombie, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
2. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Cigar           | vegafina  | alhambra  | baccarat | fonseca |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | zombie | action         | thriller    |

