.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling, magic-tricks, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, april, september
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | traveling         | skydiving  | magic-tricks     | photography         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Birthday      | december         | april  | october   | september |

