.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, punk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bolivar, swisher, aristoff
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, puzzles, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the swisher-smoker is between the fan of electronic and the fan of country##2
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of indie##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 9. the bolivar-smoker is between the fan of punk and the fan of indie##2
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | indie    | electronic | punk    |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | swisher | bolivar  | aristoff |
| Hobby           | puzzles   | drawing    | board-games        | traveling   |

