.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, old-henry, cain, davidoff
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, manager, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, june, july
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the librarian is in an even position##4
5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
9. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar      | siglo                | davidoff  | old-henry | cain   |
| Job           | software-developer | librarian | fisherman   | manager |
| Birthday   | april         | may     | july     | june |

