.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, may, december
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, helicopter, roller
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person driving the roller##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Birthday   | december | february | march | may |
| Transport   | helicopter    | airplane     | roller    | snowmobile |

