.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, cricket, swimming
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, cricketsy, superhero, musical
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person watching disaster movies##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching cricketsy movies##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
8. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
9. the person watching musical movies is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cricket      | cycling  | swimming    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | cricketsy | musical | disaster |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

