.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, fonseca, pall-mall
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
There 4 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, lemon, grapefruit
1. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the prince-smoker is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person eating pepper##2
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the japanese is between the person eating pepper and the australian##2
7. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | bongani    | fonseca | prince  | pall-mall  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Food         | lemon   | pepper      | grapefruit | broccoli       |

