.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
There 4 different types of food: lime, pear, apple, radish
City: hamburg, berlin, marseilles, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person eating radish##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lime is the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Food   | radish | lime      | pear | apple |
| City           | marseilles   | berlin  | hamburg     | edinburgh |

