3. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person who growsrose and the futuristic house##2
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the craftsman house##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| House       | futuristic   | victorian | art-deco | craftsman |
| Flower   | lily | poppy      | rose    | balloon-flower   |

