2. the colombian is between the german and the owner of the frog##2
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
4. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the frog is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Pet          | rat | frog  | pony   | fish    |
| Flower   | sunflower  | tulip     | dahlia | poppy |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

