.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, trance, classical, ambient
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, action, epic
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of trance##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of classical##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| Music-Genre           | ambient   | trance    | d&b | classical |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | adventure | action    | epic         |

