.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, subway, train
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, august, december, november
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french, nigerian
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the canadian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the canadian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the person driving the train##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | train | motorbike | skateboard | subway   |
| Birthday   | august    | november   | december     | april    |
| Nationality   | dutch  | french | canadian  | nigerian |

