.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, italian, dutch, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, snowboarding, skateboarding, rowing
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the brazilian and the chinese##2
6. the italian is on the left of the chinese##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | chinese | dutch      |
| Sport     | snowboarding   | climbing        | rowing   | skateboarding       |

 